org.apache.hadoop.hbase.master.procedure

类 ProcedurePrepareLatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.master.procedure.ProcedurePrepareLatch
  • 直接已知子类:
    ProcedurePrepareLatch.CompatibilityLatch, ProcedurePrepareLatch.NoopLatch

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
 @InterfaceStability.Evolving
public abstract class ProcedurePrepareLatch
extends Object
    Latch used by the Master to have the prepare() sync behaviour for old clients, that can only get exceptions in a synchronous way.

      • createLatch

        public static ProcedurePrepareLatch createLatch()
        Create a latch if the client does not have async proc support. This uses the default 1.1 version.
        返回:
        a CompatibilityLatch or a NoopLatch if the client has async proc support

      • createLatch

        public static ProcedurePrepareLatch createLatch(int major,
                                                int minor)
        Create a latch if the client does not have async proc support
        参数:
        major - major version with async proc support
        minor - minor version with async proc support
        返回:
        a CompatibilityLatch or a NoopLatch if the client has async proc support
